==Demographics==
In the [[2020 United States census|2020 Census]], Plainview Colony had a population of 100 people. The colony unanimously identifies as [[White people|white]] with no second ethnicity.<ref>{{Cite web |title=Explore Census Data |url=https://data.census.gov/cedsci/all?q=Plainview%20Colony%20CDP,%20South%20Dakota&y=2020 |access-date=2022-10-26 |website=data.census.gov}}</ref>{{clear left}}

